      "content": "What is Azure Backup?",
      "pos": [
        684,
        705
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Backup is the service that you use to back up and restore your data in the Microsoft cloud.",
      "pos": [
        706,
        803
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It replaces your existing on-premises or off-site backup solution with a cloud-based solution that is reliable, secure, and cost-competitive.",
      "pos": [
        804,
        945
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It also helps protect assets that run in the cloud.",
      "pos": [
        946,
        997
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Backup provides recovery services built on a world-class infrastructure that is scalable, durable, and highly available.",
      "pos": [
        998,
        1124
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Watch a video overview of Azure Backup",
