    {
      "content": "Why use Azure Backup?",
      "pos": [
        1243,
        1264
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Traditional backup solutions have evolved to treat the cloud as an endpoint similar to disks or tape.",
      "pos": [
        1265,
        1366
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "While this approach is simple, it is also limited.",
      "pos": [
        1367,
        1417
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "It does not take full advantage of an underlying cloud platform and translates to an inefficient, expensive solution.",
      "pos": [
        1418,
        1535
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "In contrast, Azure Backup delivers all the advantages of a powerful and affordable cloud backup solution.",
      "pos": [
        1536,
        1641
      ]
    },
